➜洪峰过境不眠夜，沙坪坝的12小时！
http://www.sohu.com/a/414182083_563335	6416
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200821/6c2d929231034e3990f65a1f4fdbd654.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">8月19日深夜，磁器口古镇观景平台，有星空、有帐篷、还有即将到来的洪峰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200821/c3051d7068f448259b1bbddadaadf19f.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图源丨磁器口街道</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">此次洪峰对沙坪坝区是极大考验，涉及沿江的9个街道4万多人，抗洪抢险、防汛救灾要通知到每家每户。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200821/f71e4e9deb7f49b8817f05a762406bbd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
